title: What goes up, must come down...

Here's the latest episode in my SCP animated sketch comedy. Other episodes are available [*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/art:animated-series-rookies-fifty3dragons here].

**Episode 8 - Rope Climbing Gone Horribly Wrong**

While conducting tests on a rope in Tibet that extends into the sky, the clone recruits learn the meaning of "what goes up, must come down." Inspired by [*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-144 SCP-144 (Tibetan Rope to Heaven) by FritzWillie].
